1
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,840
What you're saying is...

2
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,000
We've kept them at bay for now,

3
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:15,239
but to make your dear son give up for good,

4
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,680
this capital...

5
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,560
I'm afraid he can never return.

6
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,040
You have a way to help me?

7
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,840
I can help you,

8
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,840
but I have one condition.

9
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,599
Once it's done,

10
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,680
I want something Qi Zhi has on him.

11
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:40,760
As long as you help my son

12
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,159
get rid of him,

13
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:45,000
then we'll both...

14
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,200
get what we want.

15
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:48,879
So tell me,

16
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:50,760
what's your plan?

17
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,280
Oh.

18
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:56,760
There's a girl at a tavern in town

19
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,040
that Prince Yu

20
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:01,200
is rather fond of.

21
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:10,240
Yu'er,

22
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,039
your condition lately

23
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,240
has been getting worse.

24
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,560
Recently I've been feeling

25
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,159
dazed and groggy.

26
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:21,840
It seems

27
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,639
the only way to get rid of him

28
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,479
is to start with

29
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:28,960
that tavern woman.

30
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,639
You mean...

31
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,479
I don't believe

32
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:37,479
that after killing his beloved himself,

33
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,439
he can still hold on.

34
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,759
Ah!

35
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,400
Ugh!

36
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:49,840
Ah!

37
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,800
You...

38
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,199
You...

39
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,039
You can't kill her!

40
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,560
It seems

41
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,960
she really does mean

42
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,639
a great deal to you.

43
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,000
In that case,

44
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:15,000
she absolutely must die.

45
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:18,560
I won't let you hurt her!

46
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,080
What are you doing?

47
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,639
Put that knife down right now!

48
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,000
If you hurt her,

49
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,840
I'll take him down with me!

50
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,639
Absurd!

51
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,400
Get out here, now!

52
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,800
Ah!

53
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,479
Ah!

54
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:40,800
Yu'er.

55
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,479
Mother, I...

56
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:51,639
I didn't expect him

57
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:54,840
to react so strongly.

58
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,680
Mother.

59
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,759
Yu'er,

60
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,599
your state is unstable right now.

61
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,360
Doing this

62
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,279
is just a precaution.

63
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,839
I'm sorry you have to endure this.

64
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:21,079
I understand, Mother.

65
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,759
Huabu.

66
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,639
Come.

67
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,240
Have a chestnut.

68
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,000
Liu Heng!

69
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,720
What are you doing with my book?

70
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,360
Give it back!

71
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,000
Well?

72
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,160
Want your precious comic back?

73
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,079
Then come with me!

74
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:42,480
You...

75
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:42,920
Hey!

76
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,360
Robbery!

77
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:44,600
Liu Heng!

78
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,560
You stop right there!

79
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,199
Tonight, when Prince Yu arrives,

80
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,360
we'll strike right away.

81
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:57,959
Mm.

82
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,000
It's all on you, Yunxi.

83
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,560
Someone told me to give this to you.

84
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:06,439
Isn't this the Crown Prince's comic?

85
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:11,800
Save the Prince at the east bamboo grove.

86
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:15,199
It's gotta be Liu Heng again.

87
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,560
Listen, I'm telling you,

88
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,240
I figured out...

89
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,279
We already know.

90
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:23,639
Huh?

91
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,160
Oh, you already know?

92
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,079
Mm.

93
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,879
Who knew their chestnuts were so famous.

94
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,800
Qi Zhi, hurry up and try some.

95
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,279
Ouyang Yan!

96
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,079
Yunxi!

97
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:41,759
Where's the Crown Prince?

98
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,519
Hey,

99
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,000
quick question,

100
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,839
where is the east bamboo grove?

101
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,399
It's right here.

102
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:50,000
Right here?

103
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,240
Why is no one here?

104
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,639
Oh no.

105
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,839
Yunxi.

106
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,680
Are you sure

107
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,079
it's her?

108
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,120
Of course.

109
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,040
I saw it with my own eyes.

110
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,360
It's definitely her.

111
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,399
As long as we kill her,

112
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,800
we'll end this once and for all.

113
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,959
You want to kill her?

114
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:15,240
To make sure my son ascends the throne,

115
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:17,680
she has to die.

116
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:20,279
Yes, I told you to capture her,

117
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,560
but I never told you to kill her.

118
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,240
All I want is the late Emperor's pendant.

119
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,680
Hey!

120
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,040
You're a mother.

121
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:28,800
Could you not be so cruel?

122
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,600
Oh.

123
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,160
So,

124
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:34,199
you want the late Emperor's jade pendant.

125
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,680
What,

126
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,759
you want to be Emperor too?

127
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,160
Of course.

128
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,600
Out of all the princes in Da Liang,

129
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,480
who's more fit to rule than me, Liu Heng?

130
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,399
No one.

131
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,439
Well then,

132
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:48,040
what you want,

133
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,240
I can't give it to you.

134
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:51,800
Hmm.

135
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,680
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

136
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,839
What do you think you're doing?

137
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,879
You're double-crossing me!

138
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,439
Where's Yunxi?

139
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,800
Where's the Crown Prince?

140
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,360
Prince Yu's mother took them.

141
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:11,759
She...

142
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:12,839
She's going to kill Yunxi.

143
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,160
What?

144
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,079
Speak!

145
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,160
Is this your doing again?

146
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:17,959
Yes,

147
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:19,079
it was me.

148
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,279
Hey, wait.

149
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,079
I'll just confess on my own.

150
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,279
Prince Yu's mother

151
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:25,480
hired a hypnotist to deeply hypnotize him,

152
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,759
and fed him a strange potion.

153
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:29,160
That potion is really something.

154
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,959
Once he drinks it,

155
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,399
it can control his main personality.

156
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:33,360
Then...

157
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,839
Wait.

158
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,040
This is when you usually ask,

159
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,680
"Where is the hypnotist?"

160
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:39,040
In the south of the city.

161
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,279
The south of the city?

162
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,199
You're not going to let me go anyway.

163
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,560
So go ahead.

164
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,920
Ah!

165
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,240
Looks like to save them both,

166
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,839
we have to find that hypnotist first.

167
00:07:58,839 --> 00:08:00,000
Come to think of it, it's strange.

168
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:03,360
Why are these two consorts we've recently met

169
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,759
both so desperate to empower their sons?

170
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:07,759
It's because the other consorts are all gone.

171
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,839
That's why you find it strange.

172
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,800
What do you mean?

173
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,879
What they've fought their whole lives for

174
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,279
is now right in front of them.

175
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,839
How could they give it up so easily?

176
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,079
Let's go.

177
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:28,839
Hey

178
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:31,279
I was so cooperative, won't you save me?

179
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:37,440
You're the one who hypnotized Prince Yu.

180
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:39,799
Thirty taels per question.

181
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,600
Hey, you!

182
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,519
One hundred taels.

183
00:08:41,519 --> 00:08:43,200
Answer three of her questions.

184
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,639
Right.

185
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,360
That's me.

186
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:52,360
But I only have one question.

187
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,360
Hey.

188
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,240
How to restore his first personality?

189
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,840
Drink the antidote.

190
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,679
After drinking the antidote,

191
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:04,639
can we kill the second personality?

192
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:05,879
No, no, no.

193
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:06,600
It can only weaken it.

194
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,759
Can't kill it.

195
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,080
Why are we wasting our breath on him?

196
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:11,960
Just grab him.

197
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,799
Ah!

198
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:26,960
Hahaha.

199
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:29,240
We want the antidote.

200
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,840
One thousand taels.

201
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:43,080
Fifteen hundred taels.

202
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,440
That's enough, right?

203
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,000
Too much.

204
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:51,600
Mother.

205
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,679
How are things progressing?

206
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,080
Just waiting for you to wake up.

207
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,639
Wonderful.

208
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,039
Thank you, Mother.

209
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,279
Oh no.

210
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,559
Yu'er!

211
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,080
Guards!

212
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,159
Fetch medicine from Granny Tang.

213
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:14,759
Quickly!

214
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:15,879
How dare you slaughter the innocent!

215
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,120
Innocent?

216
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,799
If it weren't for her,

217
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:23,600
that wretch would never yield his body.

218
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:24,919
Wretch?

219
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:26,960
He's your own flesh and blood!

220
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,879
He's not my son.

221
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,120
The one who wants to be Emperor

222
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,360
is my real son.

223
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,200
You...

224
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:34,039
In just a moment,

225
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:37,679
I'll never see that unfilial son again.

226
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:38,840
Hmph.

227
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,120
What are you doing?

228
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,200
Stop at once!

229
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:46,480
Prince Yu!

230
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,240
Don't drink it!

231
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,360
Come with me, quick!

232
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:25,799
After them!

233
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,559
Someone, hurry!

234
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,440
Assassins!

235
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,240
Someone, come quick!

236
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,399
What's going on?

237
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,240
Where are the assassins?

238
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,600
There are no assassins.

239
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,879
I was mistaken just now.

240
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:43,600
Madam's orders:

241
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,279
without her permission,

242
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,240
no one may enter.

243
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,600
Come on, move, move!

244
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,039
Lock the door.

245
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,200
Have you all gone mad?

246
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,240
One more word from you

247
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,360
and I'll kill you too.

248
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:11,200
Yunxi!

249
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:14,960
Yunxi!

250
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:17,799
Yunxi!

251
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,279
Yunxi!

252
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,080
Yunxi!

253
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,480
Stop right there!

254
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,039
What happened?

255
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,879
Didn't he just take the medicine?

256
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,679
You see, I'm the kind of guy

257
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,039
who, in business,

258
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,480
never shortchanges anyone.

259
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,200
These five hundred taels

260
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,840
settle our debt.

261
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,440
Fair enough.

262
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,080
Heh heh heh.

263
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,200
Yunxi!

264
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:53,879
Yunxi!

265
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,639
Are you all right?

266
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,240
Mother.

267
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,240
I beg you, spare her.

268
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,399
Mother!

269
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,279
You wretch!

270
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:10,440
Yu'er

271
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,519
Come here

272
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:12,679
Come here

273
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,679
Kill this woman for me

274
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,240
Yes

275
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:20,759
Stop it right now!

276
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,039
She's outside

277
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,200
What are you afraid of?

278
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,759
As long as we kill this woman

279
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:35,320
we can end this once and for all

280
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:35,879
Hurry!

281
00:13:41,879 --> 00:13:42,759
You're right

282
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,759
Kill her

283
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,879
Stop!

284
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:47,399
Yunxi!

285
00:13:49,039 --> 00:13:49,879
Oh no

286
00:13:49,879 --> 00:13:50,879
Why isn't it working?

287
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:53,039
Now he has to rely on himself

288
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,200
If you must blame anyone

289
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:59,639
blame yourself for being his beloved.

290
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,240
Your Highness

291
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:05,039
Give it up

292
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:07,240
He can never defeat me

293
00:14:07,799 --> 00:14:09,159
I am the real prince

294
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,159
No

295
00:14:10,879 --> 00:14:11,960
You are not the prince

296
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,000
I am the prince

297
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,360
Aah!

298
00:14:15,559 --> 00:14:16,240
Yunxi

299
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,879
Yu'er

300
